{"tid":628480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一小時內四宗車禍　青嶼幹線近癱瘓","createTime":"2018-04-14T01:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T02:48:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cc8edaa343f5d09b49985e3a6f47b53020d36da1","tid":628480,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T01:54:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361085?_ga=2.141225778.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361085%3F_ga%3D2.141225778.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=W7b%2BWNj1u%2BV7aCy48ljdW9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=48694ff8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361085%3F_ga%3D2.141225778.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=3ad3fc21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361085?_ga=2.141225778.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n一小時內四宗車禍　青嶼幹線近癱瘓<br />\n<br />\n12.4K<br />\n要聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】青嶼幹線昨晨於1小時內發生4宗車禍，造成7人受傷，青嶼幹線往機場方向大擠塞，至近中午車龍才消散。大批旅客飽受塞車之苦，行程受阻，有人險趕不及航班。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180414/large/a0803a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180414%2Flarge%2Fa0803a.gif&h=9fd6197f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汲水門大橋昨發生6車串燒相撞。fb小心駕駛群組Hung Johnny So圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6車串燒　6人送院<br />\n<br />\n昨晨約7時半，北大嶼山公路慢線往機場方向近欣澳，一度因車輛故障而封閉，約20分鐘後完成清理後解封。不過，至8時左右，青馬大橋往機場慢線又有車輛故障，約半小時後方完成清理。<br />\n<br />\n至早上8時47分，青馬大橋快線入機場方向，3輛的士及一輛私家車連環相撞，事件中無人受傷，警員到場後封鎖快線調查約20分鐘，令交通出現擠塞。不料青馬大橋剛解封10分鐘，在9時16分青馬大橋珀麗灣向機場又有6車串燒車禍，涉及私家車及的士相撞，6人受傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n其後，於9時23分及9時51分，先後再有兩輛私家車與一輛的士，以及4輛私家車與兩輛的士相撞，一人受傷。受連串意外影響，往機場的交通出現大擠塞，運輸署宣佈汲水門大橋往機場方向的龍尾一度延至10公里外的大欖隧道及屯門公路近小欖附近。<br />\n<br />\n不少趕搭航機旅客受意外影響，市民Chloe乘搭昨上午11時15分航班往新加坡，她早於9時已乘搭的士往機場，但受連環意外影響致行程受阻。她指當時心急如焚曾作最壞打算，需改搭另一航班，幸好最終趕及，坦言鬆一口氣，「我嚟到機場真係笑晒口」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張培生"},{"pid":"cce831e0c96edd782a2630073a4ba8eca27c800d","tid":628480,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T01:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577d4f0c7cfe3deaca064b2247f35f738b759c58","tid":628480,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:07:18.000Z","msg":"市民Chloe乘搭昨上午11時15分航班往新加坡，她早於9時已乘搭的士往機場<br />\n<br />\n正常唔係2個鐘前到架咩?"},{"pid":"555a86f1f00f0c2dc4fa4a2bb2ebe9fc3c381e0d","tid":628480,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:09:28.000Z","msg":"屌等左3個字車，坐左9個字，先到荃灣，平時5個字車程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 坐西鐵一早到左"},{"pid":"352b1400df0c868b169c2c0ad1c7b311a431dbfc","tid":628480,"uid":37458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"577d4f0c7cfe3deaca064b2247f35f738b759c58","tid":628480,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:07:18.000Z","msg":"市民Chloe乘搭昨上午11時15分航班往新加坡，她早於9時已乘搭的士往機場<br />\n<br />\n正常唔係2個鐘前到架咩?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:13:30.000Z","msg":"港女 做曬網上checkin<br />\n最興一小時前到"},{"pid":"5ab3a42c4d9c263084e0f8ae3a295d99e785cf52","tid":628480,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"555a86f1f00f0c2dc4fa4a2bb2ebe9fc3c381e0d","tid":628480,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:09:28.000Z","msg":"屌等左3個字車，坐左9個字，先到荃灣，平時5個字車程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 